# 5WHY: On iOS static builds, QRC directory enumeration (QDir::entryList
# on qrc:/) can return empty results for directories without a qmldir.
# The screens/ directory in the QRC spans multiple source directories,
# so there is no single source location for a qmldir.  This file is
# aliased to qml/screens/qmldir in resources.qrc.
DashboardScreen 1.0 DashboardScreen.qml
DiagnosticScreen 1.0 DiagnosticScreen.qml
ConfigScreen 1.0 ConfigScreen.qml
ReportScreen 1.0 ReportScreen.qml
SettingsScreen 1.0 SettingsScreen.qml
SimulatorScreen 1.0 SimulatorScreen.qml
